remove(String) - 类 中的方法com.mjun.mtransition.bundle.Bundle
Removes any entry with the given key from the mapping of this Bundle.
removeActivityAnimation(Activity) - 类 中的静态方法com.mjun.mtransition.MTranstionUtil
在启动Activity或者关闭Activity，如果需要做MTransition动画时，需要在Activity.startActivity(Intent) 或者 Activity.finish()调用之后，调用该方法，来关闭默认的Activity动画
removeActivityCloseAnimation(Activity) - 类 中的静态方法com.mjun.mtransition.MTranstionUtil
因为Android默认会给Activity启动和关闭的动画，这会与MTranstion的动画冲突，所以需要在必要的时候去掉Android的默认动画 一般情况下，会在FromPage的MTransitionPage.setContainer(View, ITransitPrepareListener)主动调用一次 Because Android defaults to the Activity start and close animation, this will conflict with the MTranstion animation, so you need to remove the Android default Activity animation when necessary In general, it will be invoked once in FromPage's MTransitionPage.setContainer(View, ITransitPrepareListener)
removeActivityOpenAnimation(Activity) - 类 中的静态方法com.mjun.mtransition.MTranstionUtil
因为Android默认会给Activity启动和关闭的动画，这会与MTranstion的动画冲突，所以需要在必要的时候去掉Android的默认动画 一般情况下，会在ToPage的MTransitionPage.setContainer(View, ITransitPrepareListener)主动调用一次 Because Android defaults to the Activity start and close animation, this will conflict with the MTranstion animation, so you need to remove the Android default Activity animation when necessary In general, it will be invoked once in ToPage's MTransitionPage.setContainer(View, ITransitPrepareListener)
replaceBy(ITransitional) - 类 中的方法com.mjun.mtransition.MTransitionView
 
replaceBy(ITransitional, ViewGroup.LayoutParams) - 类 中的方法com.mjun.mtransition.MTransitionView
如果你的动画需要自定义，则需要把自定义的动画在ITransitional实现后，调用该方法，替换原生的View NOTE:必须先调用该方法才可以调用below、above方法调整顺序 If your Transition needs customization, you need to call this method after the ITransitional implementation of the custom view and replace the native View see the Demo5,6,7 NOTE: This method must be called before you call the below and above methods to adjust the order
resumeActivityAnimation(Activity) - 类 中的静态方法com.mjun.mtransition.MTranstionUtil

reverse() - 类 中的方法com.mjun.mtransition.MTransition
从当前动画进度反向执行动画 NOTE：必须先调用MTransitionPage.setContainer(View, ITransitPrepareListener)之后，才能调用该方法,否则会报错 Reverse the Transiton from current progress NOTE: You must call MTransitionPage.setContainer(View, ITransitPrepareListener) before calling this method; or will throw an exception
